{"tid":415871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英籍公民記者上傳信件  稱英國SRA正調查何君堯言論","createTime":"2017-09-27T10:30:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T10:25:09.000Z","uid":136994,"like":97,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"999a404d072b872a2d3cc03f45e848718bff441b","tid":415871,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T10:30:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170927/s00001/1506505957830\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170927%2Fs00001%2F1506505957830&d=MPVPbIJfcNROW%2BQtm8S5TXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=7347ec33\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170927%2Fs00001%2F1506505957830&h=920d7a4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170927/s00001/1506505957830</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170927/s00001/9c5ae955958893abbb5defe416894279.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170927%2Fs00001%2F9c5ae955958893abbb5defe416894279.png&h=645fccfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會議員何君堯近日接連捲入「殺無赦風波」和「資歷風波」，今日再有新發展。英籍公民記者Richard Scotford發布一封信件內容，信件是英國律師業註冊及監管機構Solicitors Regulation Authority（SRA）的回信。他在留言中指出三點，最後一點指SRA「已接受」並「正調查」網民投訴何君堯「殺無赦」言論。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">信中提到，何君堯1997年在英格蘭和威爾士註冊，但紀錄顯示他未持有執業律師證書，故此他絕非執業律師；但由於他是已註冊的律師，故SRA可以考慮有關何君堯行為失當的投訴</span>；SRA將在10月16日前再次回覆。<br />\n<br />\n值得留意的是，信中並無公民記者提及的「已接受」和「正調查」字眼。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唉，一件發生喺香港嘅事，外國律師會居然比本地律師會更加上心，真係不禁倒抽一口涼氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e94e89c44794ee2901be7821b5638394bed28336","tid":415871,"uid":41245,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T10:40:44.000Z","msg":"香港嘅事不嬲都好多人理㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好信啲五毛講香港冇人理啦"},{"pid":"94e0c78217a65500ac04355ef297fe15e9fa2d55","tid":415871,"uid":59898,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T10:41:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f113b1e377ed86465a6d0d983f5e9c76397ed7","tid":415871,"uid":41245,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T10:42:05.000Z","msg":"btw係咪可以搞到佢退休移唔到民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c735a084f3d8f99ec9b693f529cf91e697fdd41","tid":415871,"uid":18251,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T10:42:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港嘅事不嬲都好多人理㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好信啲五毛講香港冇人理啦</blockquote><br />\n係香港人唔理囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3df23ec23041345737dfe3ea2bb7f5ddaeffc86c","tid":415871,"uid":41245,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T10:52:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港嘅事不嬲都好多人理㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好信啲五毛講香港冇人理啦</blockquote><br />\n係香港人唔理囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港人唔理當初邊個send信去SRA呀？"},{"pid":"5c26d73986c3055bf419bca292068b24da14a760","tid":415871,"uid":2857,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T10:54:50.000Z","msg":"何生準備又要改網頁內容啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ca4e3f67178f6da0ea2b90a5a82ebff78e597e","tid":415871,"uid":25858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T10:56:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>何生準備又要改網頁內容啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今次抵死了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5408e0c1da0d17111877ce0204ed2f75d506efb9","tid":415871,"uid":41245,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T10:58:41.000Z","msg":"香港人唔理你點知依件事呀？<br />\n依家連登仔成日加句「香港人唔理」自以為自己係萬中無一， 好脫俗嘅香港人，出嚟諷刺人地係港豬<br />\n一日仲追求緊依啲脫俗感，香港一日都唔會好啦，上個網講句「港豬唔理」就彷彿自己唔係就自我感覺良好，第日繼續做返同一樣嘢<br />\n<br />\n成個版面都係負能量、失敗主義，依啲係香港人要做嘅嘢咩？no，失敗主義係支共想要嘅嘢"},{"pid":"ab728c56cdd042d11ef590c27a1f2aaf35bbd9c9","tid":415871,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:01:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d88933cfefe27c9dd1e397883c1dca1b25e695","tid":415871,"uid":11753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:04:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d77ff3a2b31a0fa65012d117018fb7e91faf64ad","tid":415871,"uid":130262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:06:05.000Z","msg":"有d野明明好難查，但d臭屎都係咁揚出黎。 呢壇野建制果邊都有人煮重佢米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7efe18b129d7cbcb54ed31f46b4efc7095e5ccd0","tid":415871,"uid":70946,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:10:00.000Z","msg":"位就冇硬架嘞，有咩同個官講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a96412f39d2d1926572c259196b70fe0095b4d6","tid":415871,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:10:15.000Z","msg":"推到佢佳監為止"},{"pid":"6c28e7338efacb942193de44bba6b41e18c417e7","tid":415871,"uid":19557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:10:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推到佢坐監為止</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f98ccb82f0f153de48e2e3fcaefff8d961762bf8","tid":415871,"uid":13257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:12:26.000Z","msg":"唔好再推"},{"pid":"87fc849ff3635cc4e32bc1a24dfd8b62c261a090","tid":415871,"uid":57914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:15:19.000Z","msg":"正評, 推Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/a